<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-careers.jpg');">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Careers &amp; Recruitment</h1>
    <p>Apply online &bull; Speak to team</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Content -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="careers-content">
      <h2>Osteopath jobs in New Zealand</h2>
      <span class="hiring-badge">Hiring now</span>

      <h3>Join Our Team And Embark On A Fulfilling Career Journey</h3>

      <p>We're not just offering a job but inviting you to embark on a <strong>rewarding career journey</strong> within a supportive and visionary environment.</p>

      <p>Whether you're a <strong>recent graduate</strong> or a <strong>seasoned osteopath</strong>, we welcome dedicated individuals to join our exceptional team.</p>

      <p>For graduates and junior osteopaths, we provide a structured <strong>12-month mentorship program,</strong> focusing on both clinical and professional development. Under the guidance of our Clinic Director, you'll receive weekly mentoring to enhance your skills and confidence as you progress in your career.</p>

      <p>At every stage, you'll benefit from <strong>continuous learning opportunities,</strong> a collaborative team environment, and the satisfaction of positively impacting the lives of our patients.</p>

      <p>Our competitive remuneration packages are tailored to experience levels, and we offer <strong>relocation assistance</strong> to those relocating to Christchurch. Applicants from overseas are also welcome to apply; and we can assist with the visa application and help you settle into Christchurch.</p>

      <p>Join us at Better Health Osteopathy and thrive in a community dedicated to your growth and success!</p>

      <div style="text-align: right; margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="#apply" class="btn btn-gold">Apply now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Application Form -->
<section class="section section-light" id="apply">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>Application Form</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Apply or register your interest to work at Meridian Osteopathy</p>

    <form name="career-application" method="POST" data-netlify="true" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form-container" style="text-align: left; margin-top: 32px;">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="career-application">

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Phone <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Enter your phone" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>I am a: <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <select name="applicant-type" required>
          <option value="" disabled selected>Recent Graduate / Experienced Osteopath / Other</option>
          <option value="recent-graduate">Recent Graduate</option>
          <option value="experienced-osteopath">Experienced Osteopath</option>
          <option value="other">Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Message</label>
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your message..."></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="file-uploads">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>CV/Resume</label>
          <input type="file" name="cv" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Cover Letter</label>
          <input type="file" name="cover-letter" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 16px;">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">Submit</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
